    "body": "I've investigated this issue, and it's actually a bug in the algoliasearch-helper where exclude refinement doesn't first check if there are facets at all, before reading from the result. I've tracked it in https://github.com/algolia/algoliasearch-helper-js/issues/921, so this issue can be closed",
